<td style="width: 451.25pt; border: solid #DDDDDD 1.0pt; mso-border-alt: solid #DDDDDD .75pt; padding: 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt 6.0pt; height: 26.25pt;" width="602">
<p class="MsoNormal" style="text-align: center;" align="center"><strong><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 16.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''Calibri'',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #15191e;">Superior Home Appliances – Customer Complaint Form</span></strong></p>
