<p class="MsoNormal"><strong style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;"><em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''Calibri'',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #15191e;">Example</span></em></strong></p>
<p class="MsoNormal"><span lang="vi" style="font-size: 14.0pt; line-height: 115%; font-family: ''Calibri'',sans-serif; mso-fareast-font-family: ''Times New Roman''; color: #15191e;">Type of appliance: <em style="mso-bidi-font-style: normal;"><u>fridge</u></em></span></p>
</td>
